# terraform.tfvars.example — Phase 04: Advanced HCL
# Copy to terraform.tfvars and customize before running terraform apply.
#
# NOTE: This phase demonstrates Terraform workspaces. CIDRs are
# determined by the active workspace, not by tfvars:
#
#   default workspace → 10.0.0.0/16
#   dev workspace     → 10.1.0.0/16
#   prod workspace    → 10.2.0.0/16
#
# Usage:
#   terraform workspace new dev
#   terraform apply              # Uses 10.1.0.0/16 automatically
#
#   terraform workspace new prod
#   terraform apply              # Uses 10.2.0.0/16 automatically
#
# No terraform.tfvars needed — workspace selection drives the config.
